---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
const oneOff = 'https://donate.churchdesk.com/en-gb/1/CFopNzPKS';
---
<Base
  title="Giving"
  description="Support St Barnabas Church, Ealing. We receive no diocesan, national Church or government funding — regular and one-off gifts keep this church open and its work going."
>
  <PageHeader
    kicker="Giving"
    title="Help sustain this church"
    intro="St Barnabas receives no funding from the diocese, the national Church or government. We are a self-supporting charity."
  />
  <div class="wrap page-body">
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        We do all we can to look after our finances well, including finding ways of generating
        income that fit with our values and serve our community. But we also rely on the
        generosity of our worshippers and friends.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your giving enables us to remain a hub for local events, a space for all to enjoy and
        gather, and a place of worship that is sacred, dignified and welcoming of all. If you
        are able to make a regular gift, it makes an enormous difference.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="give-ways">
      <div class="give-way">
        <h2 class="label give-way__label">Regular giving</h2>
        <p>The simplest way to give regularly, with Gift Aid handled for you, is through the Parish Giving Scheme. You can start, change or pause your gift at any time.</p>
        <a class="btn btn--solid" href={site.giving} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Give via Parish Giving</a>
      </div>

      <div class="give-way">
        <h2 class="label give-way__label">A one-off gift</h2>
        <p>To make a single donation — for the church’s work or the Food Pantry — you can give securely online in a moment.</p>
        <a class="btn" href={oneOff} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Make a one-off gift</a>
      </div>

      <div class="give-way">
        <h2 class="label give-way__label">A gift in your will</h2>
        <p>A legacy is a lasting way to help secure the future of St Barnabas for generations to come. To discuss leaving a bequest, please <a class="content-link" href="/contact-us">contact the parish office</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="page-aside">
      <strong>Gift Aid</strong> lets us reclaim 25p for every £1 you give, at no cost to you, if
      you are a UK taxpayer. If you would like to know more about how gifts are used, just ask.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .give-ways { display: grid; gap: 2.4rem; margin-top: 2.8rem; }
  .give-way { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 1.4rem; max-width: 60ch; }
  .give-way__label { color: var(--burgundy); display: block; margin-bottom: .7rem; }
  .give-way p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .give-way a.content-link { display: inline; }
</style>
